text: pitabrakd nasa a l laoh kuchea anak del thveu aoy kreab roukkhcheate be reah bek ning thveu aoy bandaul doh chenh chea roukkhcheate . trong chea anak b po ch nh robsa rsa pi robsa slab haey trong ka chea anak b po ch nhr bsa slab pi robsa rsa der . sakammopheap teangnoh ku mk pi a l laoh . dau che neah tae puok anak ngeak chenh( pi karpit) dauch me d ch tow
